{"tid":1107632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子12箱A片被丟　怒告父母求償270萬","createTime":"2019-04-15T11:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T12:01:02.000Z","uid":122,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a025f9d93e3adb432aee333d789db5aec7f6b987","tid":1107632,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190415/640_3f44ec153e461cac3e7852ccaf15e24c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190415%2F640_3f44ec153e461cac3e7852ccaf15e24c.jpg&h=05a32b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名美國男子，12箱A片、2箱情趣用品被父母丟了，憤怒提告求償86822美元(約270萬新台幣)。<br />\n<br />\n據《foxnews》報導，一名40歲男子查理(Charlie)離婚後回密西根州跟父母一起住，住了10個月以後搬去印第安納州自己住，幾個月以後，夫母把查理的行李帶去給他，但是查理發現，他龐大的收藏，12箱的A片不見了，查理說，他的父母稱把那些東西都丟了，於是查理氣得報警，說他的收常品價值28940美元(約90萬新台幣)，準備求償86822美元。<br />\n<br />\n查理的父母說，「我們整理了12箱A片和2箱情趣用品，我們從那天開始就開始把這些東西銷毀，需要花很多的時間」，並稱是為了查理才這樣做，「摧毀你的A片是為了你的精神和健康，如果我找到古柯鹼的話，我也會做同樣的事情」。檢察官在了解狀況後拒絕提起訴訟，因此查理決定找律師為自己打官司。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"f8fa9418c113e2131d68e5e94a5911052d14161e","tid":1107632,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"435e81de57ee19cba5ca9d181e3161b7fe4265dd","tid":1107632,"uid":122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o72ETE5OPwFBNS1B6/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o72ETE5OPwFBNS1B6%2Fgiphy.gif&h=3f739b0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19a99107cdf2b65e3f96b5db468904131866bb7c","tid":1107632,"uid":187905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T11:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524a7c301f7318af9edb893c97fa84f3f7cce65e","tid":1107632,"uid":233397,